{"tid":1278692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］仲有好多人未登記做選民","createTime":"2019-07-02T13:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:57:00.000Z","uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"38b61603f4ebe4d36aa6344f9f350adc2b80419b","tid":1278692,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:39:14.000Z","msg":"未登記嘅爭取時間，今日截止啦！之前已經報過年輕人登記左做選民嘅比例低過其他年齡層，大家趁仲有時間快啲登記！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=607a3c11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n【選民登記今截止】選舉處僅暫收14萬新登記 辦事處開放至凌晨收表<br />\n<br />\n新一個選民登記周期申請今日（7月2日）結束，選舉事務處指截至今日上午，於2019年選民登記周期，已完成處理約14萬2,000宗新登記選民申請，正點算近日收到的申請表格數量。按照慣例，選舉處將於稍後時間，公佈今年的新登記選民最終數字。對上一次區議會選舉、即2015年，共有26.2萬新登記選民；2016年的立法會選舉，該年則有17.7萬新登記。"},{"pid":"c287efdbc324c3f9a5985e9f3aaa0281df85357d","tid":1278692,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba59e5189b64ae9626041e041cae3b7d583f4215","tid":1278692,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推埋最後十五分鐘</span></span>"},{"pid":"e38dd6bdb33748b2a551ac0756b1c4431b8f2754","tid":1278692,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推埋最後幾分鐘</span></span>"}]}